# Parking AI local rules

- Use conda env `python39`.
- Install dependencies with `conda run -n python39 python -m pip install -r requirements.txt`.
- Run tests with `conda run -n python39 python -m pytest -q`.
- Start API with `conda run -n python39 python -m uvicorn main_api:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000`.
- Do not use Docker.
- Do not commit model files such as `.pt`, `.pth`, `.onnx`, `.engine`.
